Happy 21st Birthday Samridhi

Hey Sam!,
I hope you liked it. I know I make it really hard for you but please bear with me as I am saying it again,
"You really really mean a lot to me".
This day is not only special to you but to me as well. It is a very very big thing to me, really. This idea (website) was originally intended to be thrown at 4th of October (Our Big Day) but I changed plans, you already know about it, and I am so glad that I postponed it. The only reason was that by doing this I can add a little of my touch to your big day, thus, eliminating my absence. I am sorry I couldn't make this a family friendly thing as I really had to be myself in it
(The over-obsessed boyfriend, SIMP and your best friend).
I hope you liked that jacket even though it doesn't fit you :( but I am so happy after your reaction.

A very very Happy 21st Birthday Baby, hereby, sending you loads of warm hugs and kisses xoxoxoxo.
Enjoy your day to your best.
Yours,
Aayush
